description: AluminiumCoreLib is designed to help programmers be more efficient in C# by containing things that programmers should have and/or may need in their application.
releaseNotes:
## Changes

### AluminiumCoreLib
* Added new Element class which extends Object class.

### AluminiumCoreLib.Utilities
* Added the ability to detect if a process is running - Platform.cs
* Added the ability to read a license text file and show the license in the console - Platform.cs
* Added Date class
* Added Time class
* Removed ProjectDateVersion (formerly DateVersion)
* Renamed Utilities.Version to ProjectVersion to avoid name conflicts.
* Removed BuildDate from ProjectVersion
* Removed old Timer due to how inaccurate it was.
* Made it easier to interact with ObjectLists

### AluminiumCoreLib.Utilities.PasswordManagement
* Added PasswordGenerator class to generate secure and random passwords.
* Added wrapper SecureRNG class which wraps around an existing C# Secure Random Number Generator.

### AluminiumCoreLib.Developer
* Added new Logging class - aimed at helping log errors.

### AluminiumCoreLib.Exceptions
* Added NullVersionException - Thrown if ProjectVersion is null when it's needed.
* Added NullTimeException - Thrown if Time is null when it's needed.

### Others
* Moved Component classes to AluminiumCoreLib.Hardware.Components
* Removed all Hardware detection - All hardware detection has been moved to AluminiumCoreLib.Hardware
* Updated Java code to be closer to C# code
